<seg id=1> Dinosaur Skeleton Fossil Discovered in Xixia of Henan </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency. Zhengzhou. April 23. (Reporter Liu Yaming ) Recently, the experts and scholars concerned discovered, in Yangcheng Township, Xixia county, Henan Province, a great deal of dinosaur skeleton fossils. </seg>
<seg id=3> This is another significant discovery after an abundance of precious dinosaur egg fossils was discovered early last year in the region. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=4> The reporter learns, from Henan Cultural Relic and Archaeological Institute, that early April this year, experts concerned discovered, between two river gravel layers in Hutou Mountain and the like of Yangcheng township, Xixia county, several hundred of dinosaur skeleton fossils, including ribs, toe bones, etc.. </seg>
<seg id=5> Because of a long time of exposure on the surface of the ground, some have already broken up. </seg>
<seg id=6> Seen from the geologic strata, they all belong to the cretaceous period. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=7> According to experts' judgement, in this dinosaur fossil cluster distribution area there are still deposits of large quantity of dinosaur skeleton fossils and fossils of other species. </seg>
<seg id=8> They believed the discovery of a large quantity of precious dinosaur egg fossils in Xixia Basin is something rare in the world, and the coexistence of egg fossils and skeleton fossils in one place is even rarer. </seg>
<seg id=9> It is very significant for approaches into the classification, co-habits, reproduction behaviors of dinosaurs in Xixia, for restoring the dinosaur-age ecological environment, and for revealing the laws governing changes of the earth crust and the earth environment. </seg>
<seg id=10> The discovery of dinosaur skeleton fossils also provides an important clue for further search of dinisaur fossils according to region and hiding laws. </seg>
</p>
